      <title>银行向赛诺菲单位收购发行74.5亿欧元的债务出售</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-21/banks-launch-7-45-billion-debt-sale-for-sanofi-unit-buyout</link>
      <description><![CDATA[包括高盛（Goldman Sachs）和花旗集团（Citigroup）在内的银行已经推出了74.5亿欧元（81亿美元）的债务销售支持Clayton Dubilier＆amp;赖斯购买了赛诺菲SA的消费者健康部门的股份。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-21/banks-launch-7-45-billion-debt-sale-for-sanofi-unit-buyout</guid>
